              <i class="icon-phone" style="padding-right: 3px;"></i> (347) 729-7911<br/> <i class="icon-envelope" style="padding-right: 3px;"></i> <a href="mailto:info@flatironschool.com">info@flatironschool.com</a></p>
            </div>
